      &lt;img alt="New York City And Newark Daily Life And Economy" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/AE8vp6EYjPR7zb_sR1bedlAzZq0=/0x0:4913x3275/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73699574/2161729438.0.jpg" /&gt;
